T1  - Path release among practices in the process of path constitution: How the MP3-path appeared in the field of recorded music
AU  - Sminia, Harry
AU  - Bohn, Stephan
AU  - Sydow, Jörg
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
IS  - 8
SP  - 105073
